<% if AppConfig.test_mode %>
System is in test mode. The following email would have been sent to [<%= h @original_email %>],
but is instead being sent to the currently logged in user.
<% end %>
Dear <%= h @user.first_name %>,

The following equipment has been registered on http://www.q2012.org. Details are below.

Owner: <%= @equipment_registration.user.fullname %> (<%= @equipment_registration.user.email %>)
<%- if @equipment_registration.user != @equipment_registration.creator -%>
Registering User: <%= @equipment_registration.creator.fullname %> (<%= @equipment_registration.creator.email %>)
<%- end -%>
Registration Time: <%= Time.now.strftime("%m.%d.%Y %H:%M") %>

Name: <%= h @equipment_registration.full_name %>
District / Region: <%= @equipment_registration.district.display_with_region %>
Phone: <%= h @equipment_registration.phone %>
Email: <%= h @equipment_registration.email %>

<%= " Laptops (" + @equipment_registration.laptops.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.laptops.empty? -%>
<%= " Pads (" + @equipment_registration.pads.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.pads.empty? -%>
<%= " Interface Boxes (" + @equipment_registration.interface_boxes.size.to_s + ")<br/>\n" unless @equipment_registration.interface_boxes.empty? -%>
<%= " Monitors (" + @equipment_registration.monitors.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.monitors.empty? -%>
<%= " Projectors (" + @equipment_registration.projectors.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.projectors.empty? -%>
<%= " Power Strips (" + @equipment_registration.power_strips.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.power_strips.empty? -%>
<%= " Extension Cords (" + @equipment_registration.extension_cords.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.extension_cords.empty? -%>
<%= " Microphones/Recorders (" + @equipment_registration.recorders.size.to_s + ")\n" unless @equipment_registration.recorders.empty? -%>

Sincerely,
Q2014 Staff